Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.72,0:00:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.70,0:00:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.67,0:00:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.59,0:00:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.67,0:00:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個充滿神秘的黑色組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.94,0:00:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事件是發生在派對會場裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.72,0:00:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人物可要小心囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.29,0:00:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.82,0:00:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.71,0:00:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.67,0:00:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.06,0:01:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘狙擊手殺人事件(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.47,0:01:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒想到會那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.49,0:01:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.27,0:01:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.35,0:02:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有很多人在排隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你看 那個人剛才卻讓我先拿菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.37,0:02:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看就是那個跟相撲力士在說話的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.62,0:02:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是印染布料公司的社長吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.82,0:02:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.99,0:02:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.23,0:02:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳自己看他的手指嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.66,0:02:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.78,0:02:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說每天都在碰那些染料的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.34,0:02:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是他的手指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.87,0:02:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連他指甲裡面也都會染上顏料很難洗掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.44,0:02:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這種情況只會發生在師傅的身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.36,0:02:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道他是社長呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.36,0:02:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把他的左手跟右手比較看看嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的右手有被太陽曬黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.62,0:02:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手卻沒有曬黑對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.74,0:02:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就表示 他平常常會去打高爾夫球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.27,0:02:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果平常不是常去打球的話 是不可能那麼明顯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是師傅就沒有辦法打高爾夫球打得那麼頻繁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.88,0:02:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他就是社長了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.47,0:02:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.02,0:02:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 借過一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.25,0:02:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請你幫我簽個名好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.04,0:03:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是你的相撲迷 風兜關先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.05,0:03:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫風岩戶 你弄錯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.67,0:03:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.26,0:03:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真是嚇死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.74,0:03:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些相撲力士長得都一樣根本分不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣　我乾脆就不簽名了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.78,0:03:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.37,0:03:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太丟人了啦 你不要吃得那麼大聲好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.53,0:03:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家可是用這次派對招待券代替我幫他調查的酬勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不撈回本就划不來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就是毛利小五郎先生嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.05,0:03:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.72,0:03:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫田中幸子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.03,0:03:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能夠耽誤您一點時間談一談呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.31,0:03:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以 當然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.48,0:03:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的時間全部給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.92,0:03:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我跟妳結婚都沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.45,0:03:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請跟我到這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.76,0:03:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 到哪都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.31,0:04:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是一位社長啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.38,0:04:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.30,0:04:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做的是製造與販賣冷氣機與電腦相關的精密零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 您找我有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.70,0:04:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.95,0:04:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.04,0:04:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說我們社長收到了恐嚇信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.55,0:04:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐嚇信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.40,0:04:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人根本就沒有活在這個世上的價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.63,0:04:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會親手將你殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.06,0:04:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想請毛利先生您一定要揪出寄這封信的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.64,0:04:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.93,0:04:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那個人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.78,0:04:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是左邊那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.88,0:04:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個遞出名片的人好像是個重要的幹部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.83,0:04:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他都還對那個人卑躬屈膝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他一定是非常有勢力的人才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.03,0:04:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.39,0:04:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他是哪個大財團的小老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.24,0:04:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.86,0:05:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他應該是哪個著名政客的秘書吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.19,0:05:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是那邊的那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他太格格不入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.82,0:05:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才他就一直這樣冷眼旁觀看著每一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.55,0:05:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不是在享受這個派對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.03,0:05:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜他是做什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.92,0:05:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長有跟什麼人結仇嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.63,0:05:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.80,0:05:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為什麼不聯絡警方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.09,0:05:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為社長他向來對警方就非常反感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.77,0:05:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說警方他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.70,0:05:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是事情真的發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.05,0:05:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也不會認真的調查不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.01,0:05:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在技術上是有困難的地方啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.66,0:05:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 您對這方面倒是挺清楚的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.19,0:05:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不只清楚警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於毛利先生我也非常清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.90,0:05:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟選擇你的就是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.69,0:05:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳選擇我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用電腦調查的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.89,0:05:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現是毛利先生您最適合辦理這個案例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.30,0:05:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.87,0:06:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您會接受這個案子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.86,0:06:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過從現在開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.54,0:06:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須跟石本社長有非常密切的聯繫才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.00,0:06:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.04,0:06:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查方面的工作 我們就全權交給毛利先生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.42,0:06:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子跟幸子小姐有機會接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.71,0:06:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.57,0:06:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你拍一張照片做紀念怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐 我們兩個來照相吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.80,0:06:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  快點 這邊比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.24,0:06:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了嗎 我要照了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.31,0:06:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1+1等於…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.96,0:06:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.25,0:06:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 我是絕對沒有跟任何人有恩怨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.75,0:06:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.68,0:06:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在商場上打滾這麼多年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.58,0:06:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許真的會在不知不覺中傷了什麼人也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.73,0:06:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這絕對不是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.48,0:06:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有請一位重量級的來賓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.32,0:06:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對在場的各位說幾句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衆議院議員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.54,0:07:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高田正雄先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.47,0:07:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在請到台上來好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.87,0:07:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,議員 請往這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.34,0:07:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看吧 他果然是秘書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.61,0:07:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶 柯南你好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.45,0:07:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.95,0:07:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他們還真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.26,0:07:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡這麼黑竟然能夠一下子就照到高田議員本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許一開始就先確定了他的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.47,0:07:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能是他夾在胸口的小型麥克風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.03,0:07:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被燈光照到的時候也會自動發亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.88,0:07:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為什麼不直接走到台上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.91,0:07:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 也許是想吸引大家的注意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.89,0:07:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.92,0:07:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石本社長 借過一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.23,0:07:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.64,0:07:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.86,0:07:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.02,0:08:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新倉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.22,0:08:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,議員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.00,0:08:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.40,0:08:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這傢伙逃得還真夠快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.40,0:08:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,議員發生大事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.14,0:08:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.77,0:08:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您馬上幫我跟後援會聯絡一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.18,0:08:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是新倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說石本社長不知道受到什麼人的恐嚇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.10,0:09:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要取他性命是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.64,0:09:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就接受了他的委託
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.45,0:09:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.54,0:09:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是瞄準石本先生的子彈沒有射準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.26,0:09:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會湊巧的射中經過他身邊的高田議員的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.26,0:09:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 的確是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時在場的來賓人數眾多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會有目擊者那也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.51,0:09:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在場的來賓現在在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我們已經叫他們集中在隔壁的房間裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.62,0:09:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.73,0:09:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼可以到處亂跑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.89,0:09:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太緊張了 所以去上廁所了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.26,0:09:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.93,0:09:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件案子不用你這個小鬼插嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.19,0:09:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我剛才看到一個可疑的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.16,0:09:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.24,0:09:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人一開始的時候本來是一直靠著那面牆站著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是剛才那聲槍響以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.20,0:09:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就出現在上面那個照明控制室了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.20,0:09:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.67,0:09:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.17,0:09:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在眾多賓客之中瞄準石本先生就容易了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.01,0:10:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他是怎麼樣的一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.69,0:10:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.32,0:10:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長的就是一副壞人樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在幹什麼啊 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.66,0:10:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.72,0:10:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.99,0:10:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有一張可能是那名兇手的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.74,0:10:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手一定是這個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 不可以亂碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官 這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.17,0:10:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.61,0:10:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是高田議員當時別在胸前的小型麥克風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.07,0:10:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子彈打到麥克風了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.58,0:10:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.11,0:10:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看夠了吧 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.63,0:10:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一不留神他就跑到這裡來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.03,0:10:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.02,0:10:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到外面大廳去等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.48,0:11:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你又要到哪裡去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又想上廁所 忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.21,0:11:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去哪個廁所啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.10,0:11:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.44,0:11:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.51,0:11:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像挺緊張的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.34,0:11:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個長髮的男子到底是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.59,0:11:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石本社長的性命明明危在旦夕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.12,0:12:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她卻避著大家跟這個男人見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.43,0:12:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這其中一定有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.51,0:12:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 現在口供既然都已經問完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.33,0:12:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓我回去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.95,0:12:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石本社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.28,0:12:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您這次受的傷雖然是沒有多嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.34,0:12:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那名兇手要的是你的命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.02,0:12:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是到警察醫院去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長不會去警察醫院的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.47,0:12:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們社長有他習慣的醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.96,0:12:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且到底要不要接受警方的保護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.11,0:12:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是我們社長他的自由吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.20,0:12:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是沒錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.23,0:12:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 總得有個人保護石本先生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.90,0:12:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全權拜託您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.69,0:12:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧 我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始 我就一直守著社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼社長 去醫院吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.54,0:13:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於照片上這個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.38,0:13:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.61,0:13:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們利用出席來賓簿調查過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.09,0:13:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人的名字沒有出現在那上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.70,0:13:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.51,0:13:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經在附近這一帶設下警戒線 應該會有結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.33,0:13:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前科犯那邊 我們正在調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.75,0:13:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 你還在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.59,0:13:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你不要丟下我一個人好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 我馬上過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.21,0:13:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要到哪一家警察醫院你知道了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.38,0:13:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說他一向就討厭警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今晚開始我跟幸子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.82,0:13:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會住在一起做他的隨身保鏢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.95,0:13:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣發生什麼事我可不管你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.56,0:13:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 請坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛車子還真是豪華啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.38,0:13:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸子小姐 我看妳就坐這吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.97,0:13:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了安全起見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.08,0:13:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是坐在社長的兩邊比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.77,0:13:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.12,0:14:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖地跟我回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.94,0:14:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看 地下鐵在哪邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.54,0:14:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.43,0:14:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時會場裡面有那麼多的賓客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.40,0:14:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要射中石本社長實在太難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.19,0:14:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非得有職業級的手法才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.56,0:14:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最近黏上去的接著劑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.49,0:14:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡怎麼會有這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.00,0:14:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.21,0:14:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥克風的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照明控制室是在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.12,0:15:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這房間真豪華
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.15,0:15:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是病房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是飯店的套房都不為過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.59,0:15:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生的房間已經準備好了 請跟我過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.93,0:15:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.78,0:15:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩間房只有一個出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.69,0:15:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說有什麼人想要進入這裡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.82,0:15:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就勢必要經過毛利先生的房間才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.89,0:15:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.25,0:15:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸子小姐果然心細
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.41,0:15:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連房間的安全都設想到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.07,0:15:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們公司都是由社長一個人在負責的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.19,0:15:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長如果倒下去的話公司就一定完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.09,0:15:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來了 幸子小姐今天晚上妳睡在哪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.85,0:15:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡只有一個床而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.03,0:15:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回我自己家去睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.92,0:15:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為現在已經有毛利先生來保護我們社長了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.52,0:15:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.13,0:15:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.37,0:15:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間不錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.96,0:16:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.32,0:16:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長 您肩上的傷要不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點小傷算得了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有點擦傷罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.37,0:16:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中小姐 高田議員的事情就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.70,0:16:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我一定會儘量安排不會有疏忽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.23,0:16:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高田議員的什麼事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.72,0:16:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他的葬禮還有所有的醫療費用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說 高田議員這次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.33,0:16:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是代替我們社長死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.29,0:16:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我現在要去處理了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要走啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.81,0:16:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生剛才說過驗屍以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.41,0:16:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要和我詳細地談一談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想可能還要待一會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.89,0:16:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要不要喝點什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.16,0:16:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 啤酒好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.33,0:16:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.97,0:16:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可樂好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.99,0:16:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 有件事我可以請教你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 是什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.55,0:17:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過是用電腦才選到我幫你們調查的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.14,0:17:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是除了我之外應該還有很多私家偵探才對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會選上我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.40,0:17:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果根據過去的經驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.03,0:17:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有做偵探的本事的確是有很多人沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.07,0:17:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 如果說是哪個人比較有魅力的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.99,0:17:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那結果就很明顯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.21,0:17:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了毛利先生之外 還有其他人選嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.25,0:17:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.00,0:17:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸子小姐妳的這個決定的確做對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.45,0:17:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個可樂還真是好喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.34,0:17:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.77,0:17:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.89,0:17:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 是找您的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.61,0:17:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.61,0:17:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是名偵探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.22,0:17:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉皮還真厚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.18,0:17:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢說自己是名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.38,0:18:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是目暮警部大人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.31,0:18:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那個從宴會上消失的可疑男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.13,0:18:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在前科犯裡面找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.78,0:18:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.10,0:18:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這個男的前科可真不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.22,0:18:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫平岡志郎 今年三十五歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.35,0:18:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個握有極機密的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.04,0:18:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉此恐嚇取財的大壞蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.61,0:18:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑道上傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.86,0:18:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦盯上了就會毫不留情地榨乾對方的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.18,0:18:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還被取了綽號叫「食人魚石岡」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.08,0:18:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那石本先生之所以會被這條魚咬上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.15,0:18:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石本社長很有可能是因為什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.26,0:18:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭到平岡恐嚇了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.07,0:18:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是依照石本社長的個性來說根本不會買他的帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.21,0:18:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平岡因為這樣惱羞成怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.69,0:18:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才決定謀害石本社長的性命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.47,0:18:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這次把我這個職業殺手給惹火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要算你運氣太糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.11,0:19:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我還可以給你一個活命的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.99,0:19:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得用那把槍把我打倒才可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.98,0:19:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還奇怪怎麼到處看不到你的人影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你在這裡看電視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該睡覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.63,0:19:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽到沒有 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.79,0:19:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我關掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.57,0:19:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.57,0:19:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了 原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.44,0:19:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.92,0:19:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都上了這個真正兇手的當了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.02,0:19:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有想到這個案子當中還有這番曲折
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.43,0:19:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要證明這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.62,0:19:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前的證據根本不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 電話響了好久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.37,0:20:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.40,0:20:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓你久等了 我是毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.75,0:20:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.71,0:20:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.10,0:20:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.47,0:20:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個平岡志郎已經被人發現死掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.46,0:20:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 遺體在哪發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.51,0:20:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說好像是在他藏身的廢棄大樓的樓梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.90,0:20:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心沒有踩好墜樓身亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.41,0:20:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墜樓當時頭上的傷是致命傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.12,0:20:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是意外嗎 還是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.07,0:20:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些還不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.66,0:20:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是現在才要出發到現場去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.25,0:20:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有進一步詳細消息的話再跟你聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.23,0:20:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前鑑識人員已經進入現場調查了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.43,0:21:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.97,0:21:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在能夠確定石本社長完全安全之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.40,0:21:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就暫時不能回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.71,0:21:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.23,0:21:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叔叔打來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.98,0:21:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎 聽說我們在用立可拍拍照的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.90,0:21:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍下的那個有可能恐嚇石本社長的平岡志郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.13,0:21:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人發現陳屍在廢棄大樓裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.46,0:21:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是他殺案件啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.61,0:21:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是意外吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.27,0:21:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是從樓梯上掉下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.43,0:21:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說他在藏身的大樓裡面沒有踩好樓梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣撞到頭部死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.65,0:21:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 這不是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.45,0:21:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我想到的假設能夠成立的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.88,0:21:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是一宗殺人案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.12,0:21:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個真兇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.36,0:21:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為平岡知道這個秘密才殺他滅口的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.19,0:22:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次由石本社長受到恐嚇所引起的一連串案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.67,0:22:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乍看之下雖然非常簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.80,0:22:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是其中其實隱藏著一個天大的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.06,0:22:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會找出證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.47,0:22:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會從這個複雜糾纏的謎團之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.28,0:22:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出事實的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.48,0:23:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.63,0:23:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是這個柴田健一的女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.95,0:24:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.69,0:24:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.88,0:24:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始進入正題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.17,0:24:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.52,0:24:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.98,0:24:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.57,0:24:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘狙擊手殺人事件(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.06,0:24:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.74,0:24:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙控器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.58,0:24:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回是後篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.53,0:24:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新主題曲的歌名是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.19,0:24:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tr…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.18,0:24:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬到舌頭了
